NK001(ka)020:0: gnas brtan phyag mchod dang 'brel bar cho ga mdor bsdus bya tshul bzhugs /
NK001(ka)020:2: pan chen sh+aakya sh+ris mdzad par grags pa'i gnas brtan
NK001(ka)020:3: phyag mchod dang 'brel bar cho ga mdor bsdus tsam
NK001(ka)020:5: sangs rgyas chos tshogs lan gsum /
NK001(ka)020:6: sems can thams cad bde ba dang sogs /
NK001(ka)020:7: skyabs gnas dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:8: rgyal ba sras bcas rnams kyi byin rlabs dang //
NK001(ka)020:9: tshogs gnyis mnga' thang chos dbyings dag stobs kyis //
NK001(ka)020:10: snod bcud bde can zhing gi bkod pa'i dbus //
NK001(ka)020:11: yid 'phrog nor bu'i gzhal med khang chen por //
NK001(ka)020:12: rin chen seng khri pad zla'i gdan mchog dang //
NK001(ka)020:13: dngos bshams gzungs rig mos stobs kyis sprul pa'i //
NK001(ka)020:14: mchod sprin rgya mtshos gang zhing spyod gyur cig /
NK001(ka)020:16: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya sogs mchod pa'i sprin gyi sngags lan gsum rol mo bcas bya /
NK001(ka)020:17: spos btul zhing gdangs dang bcas /
NK001(ka)020:18: lag mthil ltar mnyam rin chen gyis spras pa //
NK001(ka)020:19: ljon shing chu mtshos brgyan pa'i sa gzhi'i dbus //
NK001(ka)020:20: rin chen las grub gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa //
NK001(ka)020:21: 0d+ma nyi zlas brgyan pa'i gdan steng du //
NK001(ka)020:22: thugs rjes rtsod pa'i dus kyi gdul bya rnams //
NK001(ka)020:23: rnam grol lam la 'god mdzad 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK001(ka)020:24: thub pa mchog dang gnas brten chen po rnams //
NK001(ka)020:25: 'khor dang bcas pa gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK001(ka)020:26: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad dang //
NK001(ka)020:27: shes rab me 'bar nyon mongs mtsho skems shing //
NK001(ka)020:28: rnam grol bsod nams zhing du bka' sdod pa //
NK001(ka)020:29: phyogs bcu'i nyan thos dge 'dun bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:30: yon sbyor mchod pa'i gnas su spyan 'dren gyis //
NK001(ka)020:31: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK001(ka)020:32: 'gro ba'i mgon po sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK001(ka)020:33: sangs rgyas bstan pa gang gi phyag tu bzhag /
NK001(ka)020:34: gsung rab rin chen sgrom gyi kha 'byed pa'i //
NK001(ka)020:35: chos skyong dgra bcom chen po bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:36: dam chos spel ba'i slad du spyan 'dren gyis //
NK001(ka)020:37: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK001(ka)020:38: thub pas bka' bsgos bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan 'dzin //
NK001(ka)020:39: yan lag 'byung dang mi pham nag na gnas //
NK001(ka)020:40: dus ldan rdo rje mo bu bzang po dang //
NK001(ka)020:41: gser be'u b+ha ra d+h+wa dza gser can mchog /
NK001(ka)020:42: 'phags pa ba ku la dang sgra can 'dzin //
NK001(ka)020:43: lam bstan b+ha ra d+h+wa dza bsod snyoms len //
NK001(ka)020:44: lam bstan klu'i sde sbed byed mi byed pa //
NK001(ka)020:45: dgra bcom gnas brten chen po de dag ni //
NK001(ka)020:46: bsod nams rin chen gling du spyan 'dren gyis //
NK001(ka)020:47: gong gi tshig rkang 'di gnyis chad dam snyam /
NK001(ka)020:48: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK001(ka)020:49: spang dang ye shes phun tshogs sangs rgyas kyang //
NK001(ka)020:50: gdul bya'i dbang gis nyan thos tshul 'dzin pa //
NK001(ka)020:51: khyad par can gyi phrin la chos skyong ba'i //
NK001(ka)020:52: gnas brtan bcu drug 'dir byon gdan la bzhugs //
NK001(ka)020:53: bde gshegs bka' lung gtsor mdzad bstan pa srung //
NK001(ka)020:54: rang don dor nas 'khor ba'i nags tshal du //
NK001(ka)020:55: gzhan don lhur mdzad gnas brtan bcu drug po //
NK001(ka)020:56: dam bcas thugs rje'i dbang gis gnas 'dir gshegs //
NK001(ka)020:57: dge bsnyen skyabs gsol bden pa'i tshig brtan pa //
NK001(ka)020:58: dkon mchog gsum gyi zhabs 'bring mchis so 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:59: bsod nams rin chen zhing du spyan 'dren gyis //
NK001(ka)020:60: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK001(ka)020:62: ji snyed su dag sogs nas /
NK001(ka)020:65: mtshungs med lta bas mi ngams shing //
NK001(ka)020:66: gser gyi mdog can mdzes pa'i sku //
NK001(ka)020:67: zhal gcig phyag gnyis skyil krung bzhugs //
NK001(ka)020:68: sa gnon mnyam bzhag mdzad phyag 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:69: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:70: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:71: gangs ri chen po ti se la //
NK001(ka)020:73: dgra bcom stong dang sum brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:75: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:76: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyi rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:77: drang srong ri yi shel nags na //
NK001(ka)020:78: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan mi pham pa //
NK001(ka)020:79: dgra bcom brgya phrag gcig gis bskor //
NK001(ka)020:80: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag mdzad phyag 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:81: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:82: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:83: lo ma bdun pa'i ri phug na //
NK001(ka)020:84: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan nags na gnas //
NK001(ka)020:85: dgra bcom stong dang bzhi brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:87: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:88: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:89: 'dzam bu gling gi zangs gling na //
NK001(ka)020:90: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan dus ldan ni //
NK001(ka)020:91: dgra bcom stong dang chig brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:93: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:94: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyi rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:95: sing+ga la yi gling na ni //
NK001(ka)020:96: gnas brtan rdo rje mo yi bu //
NK001(ka)020:97: dgra bcom chen po stong gis bskor //
NK001(ka)020:99: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:100: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:101: chu bo ya mu na gling na //
NK001(ka)020:102: 'phags pa'i gnas bstan bzang po ni //
NK001(ka)020:103: dgra bcom stong dang nyis brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:105: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:106: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:107: gnas mchog kha che'i yul na ni //
NK001(ka)020:109: dgra bcom chen po lnga brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:111: bla ma'i sku tshe bstan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:112: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:113: nub kyi ba lang spyod na ni //
NK001(ka)020:114: b+ha ra d+h+wa dza gser can la //
NK001(ka)020:115: dgra bcom chen po bdun brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:116: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag mdzad phyag 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:117: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:118: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:119: byang gi sgra mi snyan na ni //
NK001(ka)020:120: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan ba ku la //
NK001(ka)020:121: dgra bcom chen po dgu brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:123: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:124: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:125: pri yang ku yi gling na ni //
NK001(ka)020:127: dgra bcom stong dang chig brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:129: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:130: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:131: bya rgod phung po'i ri bo la //
NK001(ka)020:132: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan lam phran bstan //
NK001(ka)020:133: dgra bcom stong dang drug brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:134: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag mdzad phyag 'tshal //
NK001(ka)020:135: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:136: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:137: shar gyi lus 'phags gling na ni //
NK001(ka)020:138: b+ha ra d+h+wa dza bsod snyoms len //
NK001(ka)020:139: dgra bcom stong phrag gcig gis bskor //
NK001(ka)020:141: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:142: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:143: lha gnas sum cu rtsa gsum na //
NK001(ka)020:144: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan lam bstan ni //
NK001(ka)020:145: dgra bcom chen po dgu brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:147: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:148: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:149: ri yi rgyal po ngos yangs la //
NK001(ka)020:150: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan klu yi sde //
NK001(ka)020:151: dgra bcom stong dang nyis brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:153: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:154: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:155: ri yi rgyal po b+hi hu lar //
NK001(ka)020:156: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan sbed byed ni //
NK001(ka)020:157: dgra bcom stong dang bzhi brgyas bskor //
NK001(ka)020:159: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:160: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:161: ri yis rgyal po gangs can la //
NK001(ka)020:162: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan mi phyed pa //
NK001(ka)020:163: dgra bcom stong phrag gcig gis bskor //
NK001(ka)020:165: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:166: bstan pa bstan par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:167: 'phags pa'i dge bsnyen d+har r+m+aa ta //
NK001(ka)020:168: ral pa thod bcings glegs bam khur //
NK001(ka)020:169: snang mtha' mdun gyi mkha' la gzigs //
NK001(ka)020:171: bla ma'i sku tshe brtan pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:172: bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:173: brtson pas go bgos mthu stobs ldan //
NK001(ka)020:174: sangs rgyas bstan pa legs bsrung ba //
NK001(ka)020:175: shar lho nub byang phyogs bzhi yi //
NK001(ka)020:176: rgyal chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)020:177: zhes tshar gsum sogs ci nus /
NK001(ka)020:178: me tog dam pa sogs nas /
NK001(ka)020:180: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK001(ka)020:181: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra sa ra pra mar+d+ha ne /
NK001(ka)020:183: ar+ha te sa myak+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK001(ka)020:189: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK001(ka)020:190: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+da pa sam kra ma na
NK001(ka)020:191: badz+re sarba karma +aa ba ra na bi sho d+ha
NK001(ka)020:198: thub dbang 'khor bcas kyi mtshan nas bos te thugs
NK001(ka)020:199: dam bskul bar bsams pas mos gus rtse gcig pas
NK001(ka)020:201: mu ni mu ni ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK001(ka)020:202: zhes brgya rtsa sogs ci nus bzlas mthar /
NK001(ka)020:203: sangs rgyas sbrul pa dgra bcom 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NK001(ka)020:204: 'gro ba'i don du bstan pa skyong mdzad pa //
NK001(ka)020:205: dkon mchog gsum dngos gnas brtan bcu drug gis //
NK001(ka)020:206: bstan pa yun ring gnas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:207: thugs rje'i bdag nyid gnas brtan bcu-drug gis //
NK001(ka)020:208: 'khor tshogs srid mtsho las brgal nyon mongs med //
NK001(ka)020:209: khri dang drug stong bzhi brgya'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK001(ka)020:210: bstan pa yun ring gnas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK001(ka)020:211: sems can kun gyi gsod gyur dgra bcom pa //
NK001(ka)020:212: rigs dang zhabs ldan skye dgu'i- sbyin gnas che //
NK001(ka)020:213: 'phags pa'i gang zag chen po khyed rnams kyis //
NK001(ka)020:214: bstan pa yun ring gnas par byin gyis rlabs //
NK001(ka)020:215: bdag gzhan dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di yis ni //
NK001(ka)020:216: phan bde'i 'byung gnas bstan pa 'phel 'gyur zhing //
NK001(ka)020:217: sdug basngala kun 'byung ma lus rab spangs nas //
NK001(ka)020:218: srid pa'i rgya mtsho myur du skems par shog /
NK001(ka)020:219: bsod nams rgya mtsho yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
NK001(ka)020:220: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par dag gyur nas //
NK001(ka)020:221: smon lam rgya mtsho ma lus yongs rdzogs nas //
NK001(ka)020:222: lus can kun las khyad par 'phags par shog /
NK001(ka)020:223: tshogs gnyis mthar phyin dus gsum rgyal ba yi //
NK001(ka)020:224: phrin las bsgrub cing yon tan rnam dbye med //
NK001(ka)020:225: {la pa mnyam pa'i gdul bya smin mdzad par //
NK001(ka)020:226: mnyam med bla ma mchog gi bkra shis shog /
NK001(ka)020:227: dus gsum rgyal ba sras bcas thugs rje yis //
NK001(ka)020:228: nyan thos tshul du srid pa ji srid par //
NK001(ka)020:229: bstan pa skyong zhing 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK001(ka)020:230: gnas brten chen po rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK001(ka)020:231: zab cing rgya che'i gzigs pa po //
NK001(ka)020:233: spyan mi bzang dang rnam thos sras //
NK001(ka)020:234: rgyal chen bzhi yi bkra shis shog /
NK001(ka)020:235: phan bde 'byung ba'i gnas gcig po //
NK001(ka)020:236: bstan pa yun ring gnas pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:237: bstan 'dzin skyes bu dam pa rnams //
NK001(ka)020:238: sku tshe'i rgyal mtshan brtan gyur cig /
NK001(ka)020:239: ston pa 'jig rten khams su byon pa dang //
NK001(ka)020:240: bstan pa nyi 'od bzhin du gsal ba dang //
NK001(ka)020:241: bstan 'dzin bu slob dge 'dun mthun pa yis //
NK001(ka)020:242: bstan pa yun ring gnas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK001(ka)020:243: ces sogs kyi bkra shis ci rigs barjoda mthar rol mo bya'o //
NK001(ka)020:244: zhes pa'ng many+dzu g+ho shas bris pa dge //
